{"tid":543483,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"野豬闖第一城反轉Starbucks  警封停車場戒備","createTime":"2018-01-28T14:23:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T14:24:50.000Z","uid":1762,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2be8cf885b9a48906ca18e3262eab7533a8b913f","tid":543483,"uid":1762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T14:23:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180128/57764834\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180128%2F57764834&d=WkIEphkvF%2BttHvhkoqqae54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=37d79795\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180128%2F57764834&h=6c2b144a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180128/57764834</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n野豬闖第一城！讀者Steven途經沙田第一城商場時，赫見一隻野豬由便利店內跑出，在商場內亂竄，市民見狀尖叫躲避。野豬其後衝入Starbucks，Steven指當時店內坐滿客人，客人見有野豬，紛紛走避，野豬受驚下，撞擊Starbucks的櫃位門，企圖衝入，但不成功，牠隨後走入停車場，警員亦持盾牌趕至，正搜捕野豬。<br />\n<br />\n晚上7時許，警員束手無策，用圍欄圍封40座停車場出入口，等候漁護署職員協助。漁護署職員到場後，與警員入內搜捕，野豬在車場內亂跑，其間一度走上1樓，未幾牠企圖跳過鐵欄逃至街外，惟被鐵欄夾住，漁護署人員將其雙腳綁起制服，再放入鐵籠帶走。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n哪兒來的豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ca309b9a6c88783fc38a7d90628cb957adeee2f","tid":543483,"uid":60258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T14:24:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}